==Parodies==
* The piece &quot;L&#x27;Éléphant&quot; (The Elephant) from Camille Saint-Saëns&#x27;s &quot;The Carnival of the Animals&quot; (1886) uses a theme from the &quot;Danse des sylphes&quot;, played on a double bass.

